<font class="body">

<font class="subhead">CES Press Registration is free to qualified journalists!</font><p>

Register and receive your media credentials in the mail.  When you arrive at CES you will receive a badge holder that identifies you as a member of the press. <p> 

<font class="subhead">Three easy ways to register:</font><p>

<b>1. <a href="https://register.rcsreg.com/regos-1.0/ces01/adv/ga/live/">Register online</a><!--- beginning July 1st--->.<p></b>

<b>2. <a href="regwep.pdf">Download a press registration form</a></b>. Complete the form and fax or mail it along with proof of your press credentials to Frequita Slade (address below).<p> 
<dl>
<dt><dd>
<table>
<tr><td valign=top><a href="http://www.adobe.com/products/acrobat/readstep.html"><img src="/global_images/getacro.gif" width=88 height=31 border=0 alt="Get the Adobe Acrobat Reader"></a></td><td><font class="body">The registration form is in Adobe PDF format. You will need the Adobe Acrobat reader in order to view the file. Need the Acrobat Reader? <a href="http://www.adobe.com/products/acrobat/readstep.html">Click here.</a></font></td></tr>
</table>
</dd></dt>
</dl>
<br>
<b>3. Request a press registration form via our Fax-on-Demand Service</b> by calling the appropriate number below. Complete the form and fax or mail it along with proof of your press credentials to Frequita Slade (address below).<br>
<ul>
<li>1 888 237-7469 <font class="formInstruction">(inside the United States)</font></li>
<li>001 732 544 2865 <font class="formInstruction">(outside the United States)</font></li>
</ul>
<p>
<br>
<font class="subhead2">Register early and receive information on CES Keynotes, Exhibitor Press Conferences, Events and other CES News.</font><p>
If downloading a form or recieving a form via our Fax-on-Demand Service, complete the form and fax or mail it along with proof of your press credentials to Frequita Slade:<p>
