<tr><td valign=top align=right><font class="body">fax: </font></td><td><font class="body">703 907 7690</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top align=right><font class="body">mail: </font></td><td><font class="body">Frequita Slade<br>
CES Press Registration<br>
2500 Wilson Blvd<br>
Arlington, VA   22201-3834
</font></td></tr>
</table>
<p>
<font class="subhead2">Acceptable Documentation for Press Credentials</font><br>
<ul>
<li>copy of a published article with your name
<li>publication masthead listing you as a contributor or staff member
<li>a letter from your publisher or broadcast producer on official stationery.  
</ul><p><br><br>

<font class="subhead">Badges</font><p>
Badges for press registration will be mailed beginning mid-October, 2000. Badges for registrations received after November 17th will be processed but must be picked up onsite at one of the press registration areas.<p>    


<font class="subhead">Conference Fees</font><p>
All qualified press are automatically registered for conference sessions free of charge.  Your CES badge must be presented at each session you attend.  Please take care to keep your badge safe at all times.<p>  

<font class="subhead">Problems, questions, comments or suggestions</font><p>
CEA staff is available to assist you and appreciate your feedback, send your comments to Frequita Slade at <a href="mailto:fslade@ce.org">fslade@ce.org</a>.<p>

